CE 4363 Groundwater Hydrology/CE 5363 Groundwater Hydrology

Catalog Description

CE 4363 Groundwater Hydrology (3:3:0).. Groundwater flow; well hydraulics, development, and management of groundwater resources;
groundwater quality; mathematical modeling with available software.
Introduction to design of wells and well fields.
Prerequisite: CE 3354 or instructor consent.
